[[File:North Ward-Gost Villa.png|thumb|right|270px|''The Gost family villa (labeled <code>N57</code>) ''circa'' 1372 DR.'']]
The Gost family villa was located in the [[Waterdeep/North Ward|North Ward]] on the northwest corner of the intersection of [[Golden Serpent Street]] and [[Geltoon Street]]. Directly across the alley behind the residence was the [[Grinning Lion]] tavern. Inside the walled compound was a four-story mansion, a courtyard with some green space, and a three-story gatehouse that served as stables and quarters for most of the guards.{{Cite dungeon/128/Vampires of Waterdeep: The Fireplace Level|90}}
